sources.title: Mabels Strange Predicament (1914)
sources.description: Mabel's Strange Predicament is a 1914 American film starring Mabel Normand and Charles Chaplin, notable for being the first film for which Chaplin donned the costume of The Tramp, although his appearance in the costume in Kid Auto Races at Venice was released first. The film was directed by Normand and produced by Mack Sennett. Watch on RetroFlix.org:Â  https://retroflix.org/mabels-strange-predicament-1914/
